      "raw_text": "by United Press Leased Wirs)\n\n\nPORTLAND, Ore. Sept. 27.-It\nbecame known today that the\ntransportation committee of the\nPortland Chamber of Commerce\nwill soon start a movement to Sc\ncure changes In freight rates on\nthe North Bank railroad from va\nrious points In Washington to Port\nland. The committee held a stormy\nsecret meeting yesterday after\nnoon Attorney J. N. Teal present\ned opinions concerning the legality\nof the rates now enforced by the\nroad. and. 1t Is said. endeavored to\nshow that Portland was not getting\na square deal\""
